trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.FrameworkElementAutomationPeer"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.FrameworkElementAutomationPeer"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets the string that uniquely identifies the <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement"></xref> that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.FrameworkElementAutomationPeer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a cadeia de caracteres que identifica exclusivamente o <xref href="System.Windows.FrameworkElement"> </xref> que é associada a essa <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.FrameworkElementAutomationPeer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The value of the automation identifier is the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperties.AutomationId%2A> property, and if that isn't set, it's the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Name%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O valor do identificador de automação é o <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperties.AutomationId%2A>propriedade, e que não estiver configurado, é o <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Name%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Name%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationProperties.AutomationId%2A>

trans-unit.source: The automation identifier for the element associated with the <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.FrameworkElementAutomationPeer"></xref>, or <xref:System.String.Empty> if there isn't an automation identifier.
trans-unit.target: O identificador de automação para o elemento associado a <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.FrameworkElementAutomationPeer"> </xref>, ou <xref:System.String.Empty>se não houver um identificador de automação.</xref:System.String.Empty>

trans-unit.source: Gets the string that describes the functionality of the <xref href="System.Windows.ContentElement"></xref> that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a cadeia de caracteres que descreve a funcionalidade do <xref href="System.Windows.ContentElement"> </xref> que é associada a essa <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The help text, usually from the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ToolTip"></xref>, or <xref:System.String.Empty> if there is no help text.
trans-unit.target: O texto de Ajuda, normalmente a partir de <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.ToolTip"> </xref>, ou <xref:System.String.Empty>se não houver nenhum texto de Ajuda.</xref:System.String.Empty>

trans-unit.source: Gets the text label of the <xref href="System.Windows.ContentElement"></xref> that is associated with this <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o rótulo de texto a <xref href="System.Windows.ContentElement"> </xref> que é associada a essa <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ContentElementAutomationPeer"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The name property can be thought of as the string of text that a user would use to explain which control is being referred to.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade de nome pode ser pensada como a cadeia de caracteres de texto que um usuário deseja usar para explicar o que controle se refere.

trans-unit.source: It is important to have a textual representation for all controls in the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_gui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] so that you can programmatically refer to the control in a localized manner.
trans-unit.target: É importante ter uma representação textual para todos os controles de [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_gui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] para que você pode consultar programaticamente o controle de maneira localizada.

trans-unit.source: The text label of the element that is associated with this automation peer.
trans-unit.target: O rótulo de texto do elemento que está associado com esse ponto de automação.
